  <description><![CDATA[<p>Chalet Les Arolles is a comfortable and modern chalet with the Petite Aiguille piste and chairlift just on the doorstep, perfect for keen skiers looking to be the first on the slopes. It is a two minute walk to the resort shuttle bus or if you prefer to walk then it is approximately 15 minutes to the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/94b0461bf3c0472a89c38df58692ce28" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94b0461bf3c0472a89c38df58692ce28}" title="Les 2 Alpes">Les Deux Alpes</a> and its famed nightlife.</p>
<p>The wooden clad walls and ceilings in the chalet create a delightful Alpine atmosphere and a perfect setting for your tasty four course meals with complimentary wine. The sauna will help relax any tired muscles after a full day on the slopes and if you still have energy then use it up with a game of table tennis.</p>]]></description>
